race.description: Trader - Cabac - Robus Super Mdn Plate
race.comment: ARTGIRL (3) Flying Artie filly from the good producing mare She's Clean. Given plenty of time to mature and looks ready to go after her good trial win over 900m at Rosehill. SANT GERVASI (2) covered ground just off the speed on debut when a respectable fourth over 1000m at Hawkesbury. Doesn't have to improve much from the inside draw to take a hand in the finish. CONFIDENTIALITY (4) kept safe in betting on debut when sitting up on the speed for a tenacious third over 1000m at Hawkesbury. Looks to have further upside for this and sure to be thereabouts. DOLCE VITA (5) I Am Invincible filly from the good producing mare Dream Play on debut for the Baker yard. Fitted with the two trials and shapes as a leading player.
